                    <h3>Coram Deo</h3>
                </a>
                <p>Coram Deo is a Latin phrase translated "in the presence of God" from Christian theology which summarizes the idea of Christians living in the presence of, under the authority of, and to the honor and glory of God.<a href="#cd"><sup>1</sup></a></p>
            </div>
