                </a>
                <p>Abundant joy and total commitment to the glory of God is the basic idea of Christian Hedonism<a href="#ch"><sup>2</sup></a>.  The term itself comes from <a href="http://www.desiringgod.org/articles/what-is-christian-hedonism" target="_blank">the writings of John Piper</a>.  </p>
