                <a href="~/WakeUpToTheWord/WhatIsTheHolySpirit">
                    <h3>The Holy Spirit</h3>
                </a>
                <p>The Holy Spirit is a person like being which is full of the power of God and is God just as Jesus was.  Billy Graham states "He is a mighty Person, the Holy Spirit of God." <a href="#sp"><sup>3</sup></a></p>
